AnodeGeom	 ../../agfiles/AnodeGeometry	   location of anode geometry file
ELossBins	 300			   Number of bins for y axis
MaxELoss	 5			   Max y value [MeV]
strip		 -1			   Strip where reaction takes place. Use -1 for unreacted beam
Eres		 0.0			   Energy 'noise' level (sigma) in each strip [MeV]
beam		 17F			   Use "AEl" notation, e.g. 17F where A=17 El(ement) = F
Kb		 42.0			   Beam energy as it enters the dead gas layer [MeV] (Exp=42.59)
KbFWHM		 5.0			   Beam energy FWHM [MeV]
target		 4He			   
compound	 21Na			   
NumEvapPart	 1			   Number of evaporated particles. E.g. 1 for 17F(4He,1H)
evap0Name	 1H			   
evap0Color	 632			   Integer. See ROOT colors (red=632, blue=600, magenta=616, green=416)
res0Name	 20Ne
