dEdxScaleRes0	 1.0			   Heavy particle stopping power scale factor
NEvents		 1000			   Number of events simulated
Wait		 0			   Wait between simulated events? 1=yes, 0=no
Update		 0			   Update graphics between simulated events? 1=yes, 0=no
MaxTime		 2000			   Maximum time for an event [ns]
